            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Surviving in Antarctica and the Arctic Circle is a challenge that requires specialized equipment, and that's especially true when it comes to the vehicles required to traverse some of the harshest and coldest terrain on the planet. For the ",
